{"tid":236872,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(絲打入)我應唔應該同BF分手？","createTime":"2017-05-10T04:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T06:21:47.000Z","uid":28287,"like":1,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a788892b041b1af4726752ece9bc42df9b8f151","tid":236872,"uid":28287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"都已經唔止一件事架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n雖然BF行街睇戲食飯洗費都係佢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係我覺得我BF愈來愈多缺點 <br />\n<br />\n以前都唔覺有咁多架(👉🏻👈🏻覺得心淡）<br />\n<br />\n識左男友兩個幾月喇 之前佢會應承我一個月只會翻一次伯母屋企 （因為我之前投訴過佢媽媽好dirty同縮骨 每次都拎埋d隔夜餸出黎招呼我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲要撈埋d隔夜飯落去 真係完全唔當我係未來新抱 真係好過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n而家BF話今個月要去三次auntie到食飯 又要同佢飲茶 （佛誕 母親節 端午節）我真係唔知點同d閨蜜交待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n絲打們你地話我點忍受到去個寒酸伯母到食飯 仲要係三次添啊。  （👉🏻👈🏻覺得想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n我衣家完全唔覺得BF緊張過我在乎過我 我應唔應該同佢分手（👉🏻👈🏻覺得難已抉擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"f1963fe9ba4a0bec0aee917b194b3e43bb1e346b","tid":236872,"uid":28287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:35:56.000Z","msg":"借男閨蜜account打 希望絲打幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73210759544c15978398af2d4a182ac6a9bcbcd7","tid":236872,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:39:29.000Z","msg":"你想拎自己依家地位同人地老母個地位比？？<br />\n咩叫你係未來新抱 娶硬你/嫁硬比佢？？<br />\n訂左婚先講啦<br />\n笑雞"},{"pid":"1a28d9dac5d7c1e9da1ea0f366e66042ee7250cb","tid":236872,"uid":28287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:40:19.000Z","msg":"佢完全唔理我d opinions 點會有BF咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c554f074929997818e6f93